I understand you might be hesitant to share information. However, I can only help create an effective customer feedback survey if I understand some basic details about your product or service. Without this information, I won't be able to help develop relevant survey questions that will give you meaningful insights.

Would you be willing to at least tell me what type of product or service you're looking to gather feedback about? It can be as general as you'd like to start with.
